{"tid":1978070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［我要鬥黃］ 鬥黃不是這樣鬥的","createTime":"2020-04-18T12:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T12:30:16.000Z","uid":309148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc0b8f9df08696fcc94ad2c80fd9f7198bdc004","tid":1978070,"uid":309148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"要自己同自己鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起琴日 我今日又更加黃咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該好快就會黃到發光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你呢 連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起琴日嘅你 <br />\n今日嘅你 係咪更加黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你今日黃咗未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬥藍就唔同喇 鬥藍一定要同人鬥先過癮<br />\n「你唔翻廣州住 你敢話自己係藍？偽藍！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥黃就自己同自己鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬥藍就一定同其他人鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1ffbec5656a3acd9a39a6cc1b187ba7d5bf985","tid":1978070,"uid":355971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"59bd1e14bd2ad98f78205d9465b340aa31063447","tid":1978070,"uid":36444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}